gulf are some minesweepers belonging to britain and france britain 
plans to withdraw its vessels in the next week or two 
shevardnadze refused to say what he would discuss with khomeini 
it is natural that we cannot avoid urgent and important 
issues he said in clear reference to the stalled peace talks 
